About Us

Who We Are?

The Digital Career Institute was born as an initiative to integrate refugees into digital jobs. Today it is committed to train anyone who wants to pursue a tech career.

Passion

We’re driven by a passionate belief in the work we do. This passion can be found in our classrooms, our office and in the work of our students. We’re proud to have created a buzzing environment driven by a sense of purpose and dedication.
